    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone looking for a dependable daily driver without the premium price tag of a newer model. The engine and transmission are in good working order, though you may notice some minor cosmetic wear on the interior and a few exterior scratches consistent with its age. While it drives well, it could benefit from a basic tune-up and some detailing to bring it back to its best. Overall, it's a solid, functional car that offers great value for its price.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
